# Ignore everything by default; whitelist only the config we want to track.
# ~/.agents may accumulate runtime state (caches, sessions, credentials)
# depending on the agent runtime -- none of which belongs in git.
*
!.gitignore
!AGENTS.md
!skills/
!skills/**
# omarchy drops its own skill symlink here once ~/.agents/skills is folded into
# this package; it points at the omarchy install and is recreated by init, not
# tracked.
skills/omarchy
